These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, gardening, drawing, card-games
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person eating mango is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Hobby   | gardening  | filmmaking     | drawing   | card-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
4 different games are played: chess, mah-jongg, bridge, poker
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Game   | bridge    | mah-jongg      | chess | poker |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, rock-climbing, traveling, writing
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, aconite, orchid, poppy
1. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who growsdahlia##1
3. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | fishing | writing | traveling   | rock-climbing |
| Flower   | dahlia   | orchid | poppy | aconite         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, drama, western
House: palace, victorian, cottage, modern
1. the victorian house is the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the cottage house##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the palace house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | western | disaster | action  | drama      |
| House         | victorian | modern   | cottage | palace |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cucumber, kiwi, pineapple
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, black, amber, brown
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
4. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pineapple | kiwi | cucumber | cauliflower |
| Color    | purple       | brown | amber | black     |

