.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, mexican, nigerian, pakistani
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, fanta, cola, almond-milk
1. the mexican is on the far right##1
2. the pakistani is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | nigerian | dutch | mexican |
| Beverage           | lemonade      | cola | almond-milk | fanta    |

