.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, designer, entrepreneur, musician
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, basketball, swimming, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the designer##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the musician##1
3. the designer is on the right of the chef##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | entrepreneur | chef      | designer | musician |
| Sport   | handball          | basketball | swimming     | ice-hockey    |

