2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
4. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | cola | milk  | hot-chocolate | sprite |
| Color   | grey | turquise | purple          | brown    |

