.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, sprite, water
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, musician, architect, security-guard
1. the architect is on the right of the librarian##1
2. the security-guard is on the right of the architect##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | sprite | milk  | hot-chocolate | water |
| Job   | librarian  | architect | security-guard           | musician   |

