.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian, japanese, malaysian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, september, january, november
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the malaysian##1
5. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | japanese | malaysian     | argentine | egyptian |
| Birthday         | november | september | december   | january   |

