.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-16::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, davidoff, ritmeester, dannemann
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, family, scientific, thriller
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the prince-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
5. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4        |
| Cigar           | prince | dannemann    | davidoff    | ritmeester |
| Movie-Genre   | family      | scientific | documentary | thriller       |

