1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles | rock-climbing | video-games | cooking |
| Pet   | pony     | hedgehog    | turtle      | snake   |

