.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, mexican, nigerian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, soy-milk, milk
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the nigerian##1
3. the american is on the left of the mexican##1
4. the nigerian is the person drinking milk##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican | argentine | nigerian   |
| Beverage     | soy-milk  | 7up    | coffee       | milk |

 